name: Oh Baby! Baby Shower | Invitations
description:
Oh boy! Baby Boy! A fun and modern invitation that sets the tone for a baby girl or baby boy shower. Oh baby! Baby Girl! can be designed in colors of your choosing for a baby girl shower. Each set includes 25 personalized matte flat cards printed on heavy white card stock and 25 envelopes with printed return address.

>> A6 card size that measures 4.5" x 6.25"

>> White envelopes with printed return address

>> One digital proof for approval before printing

name: Oh Baby! Baby Shower | Thank You Gift Set
description:
Gift this beautiful coordinating thank you card set to the mom-to-be and save her much needed time by having her return address printed on each envelope. Each gift set includes 16 personalized matte flat cards printed on heavy white card stock and 16 envelopes with printed return address all packaged with a matching ribbon.

>> A2 card size that measures 4.25" x 5.5"

>> White envelopes with printed return address

>> One digital proof for approval before printing
